# ============================================
# Docker Ignore File
# ============================================
# Excludes unnecessary files from Docker builds
# Interview Note: Reduces build context size and improves build speed
# ============================================

# Git
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Build outputs
**/bin
**/obj
**/out

# IDE & Editor
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
*~

# User-specific files
*.user
*.userosscache
*.suo

# NuGet
**/.nuget
**/packages

# Test results
**/TestResults

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docker files (not needed in container)
**/Dockerfile*
**/.dockerignore
**/docker-compose*

# Documentation (optional - include if needed in container)
**/README.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/LICENSE

# Database files (we use volume mounts)
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal
**/*.sqlite

# Logs
**/*.log
**/logs

# Temp files
**/tmp
**/temp
**/*.tmp

# Secrets (never include in images!)
**/*.pfx
**/*.pem
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/secrets.json

# Migration files (include these if needed for production)
# Migrations/
